@BritneyDiamond4 I felt fine afterwards but that first day I thought I was dieing.  But I am a guy and we are wimps when we get sick.  
I work in health care so I was give my vaccine back in February.
@BritneyDiamond4 Hope you feel better than I did.  I felt like I had the worst case of the flu for 24 hours after I got my second moderns dose.
@BritneyDiamond4 random and not related to the tweet, but the pink nails look sooo cute! and CONGRATS on the vaccine pretty girl! 🍷😘🔥❤️
